# cad / cadquery

Wrapper for CadQuery — Python BREP modeling. Upstream: https://cadquery.readthedocs.io

controls do
  cad.width: { label: "Width (mm)", type: "text" }
  cad.height: { label: "Height (mm)", type: "text" }
  cad.depth: { label: "Depth (mm)", type: "text" }
end

## Setup

```bash
pip install cadquery
python3 enclosure.py
```

## Failure modes

- **OCP install** — CadQuery needs OpenCascade bindings; use conda/mamba if pip fails.
